{"tid":932571,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【統計學】三桶油與國際油價關系。","createTime":"2018-12-07T23:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T05:16:01.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7c1c30780bab9e9839fe933623ba476e930da940","tid":932571,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"坊間經常說三桶油中的中國海洋石油(883)，其股價對油價升跌最敏感。另外兩桶油，中國石油股份(857)及中國石油化工(386)，其敏感度又如何呢？<br />\n<br />\n利用Correlation coefficient來量度四者的線性關係。先重溫一下，若系數是1代表完全相關，0代表沒有關係，-1代表反向完全相關。<br />\n<br />\n中海油的系數是0.85，<br />\n較中石油的0.68和<br />\n中石化的0.71為高。<br />\n<br />\n若然只看2018年頭11個月，3間公司的系數分別是0.79，0.64和0.65，趨勢一樣但關係程度卻略為下降。"},{"pid":"575853fb4c9dcce60bfbe2b703fe3e6d6ef495c8","tid":932571,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T23:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/08/075333_388adc7682731d89b0cc71b0b12c4807.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F08%2F075333_388adc7682731d89b0cc71b0b12c4807.png&h=8a4d4cf2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56a737a1514d606cfcb9643b11ad4b770b0d3cb8","tid":932571,"uid":121610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"中海油主打上游<br />\n中石化主打下游"},{"pid":"c5fc79b59971ece01019e97e94abb19618e88a94","tid":932571,"uid":52869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"如果用紐約期油比較, 系數會升定跌?"},{"pid":"41c69ac6f2cf8064c5c972840694b4f957cc7177","tid":932571,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T05:16:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}